{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":800,"text":"(Mosquito buzzing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":10040,"text":"(Swat)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13480,"text":"Gotcha."},{"time":15960,"text":"Mosquitoes."},{"time":17880,"text":"I hate them."},{"time":20120,"text":"Don't you?"},{"time":21960,"text":"That awful buzzing sound at night\naround your ears"},{"time":24600,"text":"that drives you absolutely crazy?"},{"time":27280,"text":"Knowing that she wants\nto stick a needle in your skin"},{"time":29800,"text":"and suck out your blood?"},{"time":31520,"text":"That's awful, right?"},{"time":33280,"text":"In fact, there's only one good thing\nI can think of when it gets to mosquitoes."},{"time":39000,"text":"When they fly into our bedroom at night,"},{"time":41800,"text":"they prefer to bite my wife."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43601,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44840,"text":"But that's fascinating, right?"},{"time":46320,"text":"Why does she receive more bites than I do?"},{"time":50600,"text":"And the answer is smell,"},{"time":53040,"text":"the smell of her body."},{"time":55120,"text":"And since we all smell different\nand produce chemicals on our skin"},{"time":59000,"text":"that either attract or repel mosquitoes,"},{"time":61960,"text":"some of us are just\nmore attractive than others."},{"time":65360,"text":"So my wife smells nicer than I do,\nor I just stink more than she does."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71560,"text":"Either way, mosquitoes find us in the dark\nby sniffing us out. They smell us."},{"time":77800,"text":"And during my PhD,\nI wanted to know exactly"},{"time":81120,"text":"what chemicals from our skin\nAfrican malaria mosquitoes use"},{"time":85224,"text":"to track us down at night."},{"time":87680,"text":"And there's a whole range\nof compounds that they do use."},{"time":90760,"text":"And this was not going to be an easy task."},{"time":93600,"text":"And therefore we set up\nvarious experiments."},{"time":97640,"text":"Why did we set up these experiments?"},{"time":99840,"text":"Because half the world's population"},{"time":102160,"text":"runs the risk of contracting\na killer disease like malaria"},{"time":106480,"text":"through a simple mosquito bite."},{"time":108840,"text":"Every 30 seconds,\nsomewhere on this planet,"},{"time":111280,"text":"a child dies of malaria,"},{"time":113760,"text":"and Paul Levy this morning,\nhe was talking about the metaphor"},{"time":116680,"text":"of the 727 crashing\ninto the United States."},{"time":119200,"text":"Well, in Africa, we have\nthe equivalent of seven jumbo 747s"},{"time":124880,"text":"crashing every day."},{"time":127320,"text":"But perhaps if we can attract\nthese mosquitoes to traps,"},{"time":130639,"text":"bait it with our smell,"},{"time":132240,"text":"we may be able\nto stop transmission of disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136360,"text":"Now, solving this puzzle\nwas not an easy thing,"},{"time":138600,"text":"because we produce hundreds\nof different chemicals on the skin,"},{"time":141600,"text":"but we undertook\nsome remarkable experiments"},{"time":144280,"text":"that managed us to resolve\nthis puzzle very quickly indeed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147600,"text":"First, we observed\nthat not all mosquito species"},{"time":150960,"text":"bite on the same part of the body."},{"time":153600,"text":"Strange."},{"time":154840,"text":"So we set up an experiment"},{"time":156440,"text":"where we put a naked volunteer\nin a large cage,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":159821,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160860,"text":"and in that cage, we released mosquitoes"},{"time":163320,"text":"to see where they were biting\non the body of that person."},{"time":166600,"text":"And we found some remarkable differences."},{"time":169000,"text":"On the left here you see the bites"},{"time":172040,"text":"by the Dutch malaria mosquito\non this person."},{"time":174320,"text":"They had a very strong preference\nfor biting on the face."},{"time":177840,"text":"In contrast, the African malaria mosquito"},{"time":180360,"text":"had a very strong preference for biting\nthe ankles and feet of this person."},{"time":185560,"text":"And that, of course,\nwe should have known all along,"},{"time":188040,"text":"because they're called\nmosqui-toes, you see?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":191200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":192560,"text":"That's right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193800,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":196080,"text":"And so we started\nfocusing on the smell of feet ..."},{"time":201240,"text":"on the smell of human feet,"},{"time":203080,"text":"until we came across\na remarkable statement in the literature"},{"time":206840,"text":"that said that cheese smells after feet"},{"time":210640,"text":"rather than the reverse."},{"time":212840,"text":"Think of it."},{"time":214320,"text":"And this triggered us\nto do a remarkable experiment."},{"time":216773,"text":"We tried, with a tiny little piece\nof Limburger cheese,"},{"time":221840,"text":"which smells badly after feet,"},{"time":224240,"text":"to attract African malaria mosquitoes."},{"time":226400,"text":"And you know what? It worked."},{"time":229440,"text":"In fact, it worked so well"},{"time":232440,"text":"that now we have a synthetic mixture\nof the aroma of Limburger cheese"},{"time":237000,"text":"that we're using in Tanzania"},{"time":238800,"text":"and has been shown there"},{"time":240040,"text":"to be two to three times\nmore attractive to mosquitoes than humans."},{"time":244760,"text":"Limburg, be proud of your cheese,"},{"time":248280,"text":"as it is now used\nin the fight against malaria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251440,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":258279,"text":"That's the cheese, just to show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261399,"text":"My second story is remarkable as well."},{"time":264720,"text":"It's about man's best friend.\nIt's about dogs."},{"time":267960,"text":"And I will show you how we can use dogs\nin the fight against malaria."},{"time":272880,"text":"One of the best ways of killing mosquitoes"},{"time":275760,"text":"is not to wait until\nthey fly around like adults"},{"time":279080,"text":"and bite people and transmit disease."},{"time":281800,"text":"It's to kill them when they're still\nin the water as larvae."},{"time":285920,"text":"Why?"},{"time":287160,"text":"Because they are just like the CIA."},{"time":290480,"text":"In that pool of water,\nthese larvae are concentrated."},{"time":294480,"text":"They're all together there.\nThey are immobile."},{"time":297160,"text":"They can't escape from that water."},{"time":298840,"text":"They can't fly."},{"time":300440,"text":"And they're accessible."},{"time":303160,"text":"You can actually walk up to that pool\nand you can kill them there, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":308120,"text":"So the problem that we face with this"},{"time":311760,"text":"is that, throughout the landscape,\nall these pools of water with the larvae,"},{"time":315680,"text":"they are scattered all over the place,"},{"time":317680,"text":"which makes it very hard\nfor an inspector like this"},{"time":320920,"text":"to actually find all these breeding sites\nand treat them with insecticides."},{"time":325040,"text":"And last year we thought very, very hard,\nhow can we resolve this problem?"},{"time":329960,"text":"Until we realized that just like us --\nwe have a unique smell --"},{"time":334440,"text":"mosquito larvae\nalso have a very unique smell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338480,"text":"And so we set up another crazy experiment,"},{"time":340680,"text":"because we collected\nthe smell of these larvae,"},{"time":343040,"text":"put it on pieces of cloth,\nand then did something very remarkable."},{"time":346960,"text":"Here we have a bar with four holes"},{"time":349400,"text":"and we put the smell\nof these larvae in the left hole."},{"time":352200,"text":"Oh, that was very quick."},{"time":353440,"text":"And then you see the dog.\nIt's called Tweed. It's a border collie."},{"time":356600,"text":"He's examining these holes\nand now he's got it already."},{"time":359240,"text":"He's going back to check\nthe control holes again,"},{"time":361600,"text":"but he's coming back to the first one,"},{"time":363480,"text":"and now he's locking into that smell,"},{"time":365320,"text":"which means that now,\nwe can use dogs with these inspectors"},{"time":368960,"text":"to much better find the breeding sites\nof mosquitoes in the field,"},{"time":372200,"text":"and therefore have\na much bigger impact on malaria."},{"time":375320,"text":"This lady is Ellen van der Zweep."},{"time":376960,"text":"She's one of the best\ndog trainers in the world,"},{"time":379223,"text":"and she believes\nthat we can do a lot more."},{"time":382160,"text":"Since we also know that people\nthat carry malaria parasites"},{"time":385640,"text":"smell different compared to people\nthat are uninfected,"},{"time":388520,"text":"she's convinced that we can train dogs\nto find people that carry the parasite."},{"time":394800,"text":"That means that in a population\nwhere malaria has gone down all the way"},{"time":398240,"text":"and there's few people\nremaining with parasites,"},{"time":400680,"text":"that the dogs can find these people,"},{"time":402440,"text":"we can treat them with antimalarial drugs\nand give the final blow to malaria."},{"time":406360,"text":"Man's best friend\nin the fight against malaria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410080,"text":"My third story is perhaps\neven more remarkable ..."},{"time":413280,"text":"and, I should say, has never been shown\nto the public until today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416780,"text":"(Audience cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417805,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":419760,"text":"It's a crazy story, but I believe\nit's perhaps the best and ultimate revenge"},{"time":424760,"text":"against mosquitoes ever."},{"time":426440,"text":"In fact, people have told me"},{"time":427960,"text":"that now they will enjoy\nbeing bitten by mosquitoes."},{"time":432520,"text":"And the question of course is,"},{"time":434080,"text":"what would make someone\nenjoy being bitten by mosquitoes?"},{"time":437800,"text":"And the answer I have right here ..."},{"time":441080,"text":"in my pocket --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442546,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":443571,"text":"if I get it."},{"time":445960,"text":"It's a tablet."},{"time":448000,"text":"A simple tablet,"},{"time":449240,"text":"and when I take it with water ..."},{"time":452480,"text":"it does miracles."},{"time":456960,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464360,"text":"Now, let me show you how this works."},{"time":467960,"text":"Here in this box, I have a cage"},{"time":472014,"text":"with several hundred\nhungry female mosquitoes ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479016,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":480320,"text":"that I'm just about to release."}]},{"cues":[{"time":482800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":484600,"text":"Just kidding, just kidding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485965,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487360,"text":"What I'm going to show you\nis, I'm gonna stick my arm into it"},{"time":490440,"text":"and I will show you\nhow quickly they will bite."},{"time":493480,"text":"There we go."},{"time":495480,"text":"Don't worry, I do this\nall the time in the lab."},{"time":498320,"text":"There we go."},{"time":500560,"text":"OK."},{"time":502240,"text":"Now, on the video --"},{"time":505320,"text":"on the video here,"},{"time":507160,"text":"I'm going to show you\nexactly the same thing,"},{"time":509320,"text":"except that what\nI'm showing you on the video"},{"time":511480,"text":"happened one hour after I took the tablet."},{"time":514799,"text":"Have a look."},{"time":516720,"text":"That doesn't work."},{"time":517960,"text":"OK. Sorry about that."},{"time":519600,"text":"I'm sticking in my arm,\nI'm giving them a big juicy blood meal,"},{"time":522600,"text":"I'm shaking them off,\nand we follow them through time"},{"time":525120,"text":"to see these mosquitoes\nget very, very sick indeed,"},{"time":527640,"text":"here shown in fast motion."},{"time":529920,"text":"And three hours later,\nwhat we see at the bottom of the cage"},{"time":533880,"text":"is dead mosquitoes ..."},{"time":536000,"text":"very dead mosquitoes."},{"time":538800,"text":"And I'm going to say,\nladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":540840,"text":"we have swapped the cards with mosquitoes."},{"time":542864,"text":"They don't kill us. We kill them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546440,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":555640,"text":"Now --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":557960,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":561160,"text":"Maastricht, be prepared."},{"time":563400,"text":"Now, think of what we can do with this."},{"time":565320,"text":"We can actually use this\nto contain outbreaks"},{"time":567480,"text":"of mosquito-born diseases,\nof epidemics, right?"},{"time":571160,"text":"And better still,\nimagine what would happen"},{"time":573200,"text":"if, in a very large area, everyone would\ntake these drugs, for just three weeks."},{"time":577920,"text":"That would give us an opportunity"},{"time":579560,"text":"to actually eliminate\nmalaria as a disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582360,"text":"So cheese, dogs and a pill\nto kill mosquitoes."},{"time":586320,"text":"That's the kind of out-of-the-box\nscience that I love doing ..."},{"time":590160,"text":"for the betterment of mankind,"},{"time":592160,"text":"but especially for her,"},{"time":593800,"text":"so that she can grow up\nin a world without malaria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597720,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598960,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}